### REGISTER USER
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "email": "admin@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### Login API
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}